07 Feb 2013

Playlist: Jan 2013

Discovered Erased Tapes this month, and in particular, Nils Frahm. Four Tet's latest release, 0181 is lovely, and his Return to Plastic People mix is superb: Rocketnumbernine – Matthew and Toby (Four Tet remix) and J&W Beat by Floating Points are highlights.
